nacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Vitamin E 500 IU Size Size 150 capsules Good health changes everything—support your cardiovascular and antioxidant needs with Blackmores Vitamin E 500 IU. This natural-source formula delivers vitamin E to help reduce free radical damage to body cells, supporting your cells against oxidative stress caused by lifestyle and environmental factors. It also helps maintain healthy cholesterol and supports the maintenance of healthy blood lipids, making it a smart choice for heart health. Additionally, it contributes to blood vessel health and helps maintain vitamin E levels in the body, especially where dietary intake may be insufficient. Blackmores Vitamin E 500 IU supports general health and wellbeing, is suitable for daily use. This formula is also Halal certified. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Healthy Cholesterol Antioxidant for Free Radical Damage Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports healthy cholesterol. Maintains healthy blood lipids. Is an antioxidant to help protects cells from free radical damage. Helps maintain vitamin E levels in the body. Maintains general health and wellbeing. One-a-day dose. Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you are pregnancy or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Do not use if you have pre-existing severe heart disease (such as heart attack or stroke). If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports healthy cholesterol. Maintains healthy blood lipids. Is an antioxidant to help protects cells from free radical damage. Helps maintain vitamin E levels in the body. Maintains general health and wellbeing. One-a-day dose. Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you are pregnancy or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Do not use if you have pre-existing severe heart disease (such as heart attack or stroke). If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: d-alpha-tocopherol 335 mg equivalent vitamin E 500 IU Vitamin E 500 IU Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back