 for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Eye Health Macula Health No Added Gluten No Added Yeast No Added Dairy Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Relieves dry eyes. Helps reduce visual fatigue from prolonged screen use. Supports healthy eye function and vision. Supports eye retina and macula health. Supports vitality. Supports blood vessel and capillary health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Contains omega-3 with high concentrate DHA. Dosage Adults General eye health : Take 1 capsule once a day. Targeted benefits: Take 2 capsules once a day. Do not exceed 2 capsules in 24 hours. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions before use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Relieves dry eyes. Helps reduce visual fatigue from prolonged screen use. Supports healthy eye function and vision. Supports eye retina and macula health. Supports vitality. Supports blood vessel and capillary health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Contains omega-3 with high concentrate DHA. Adults General eye health : Take 1 capsule once a day. Targeted benefits: Take 2 capsules once a day. Do not exceed 2 capsules in 24 hours. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions before use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. The Blackmores difference Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Docosahexaenoic acid (DHA)-rich oil derived from microalgae Schizochytrium sp. 180 mg equivalent docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 126 mg Tagetes erecta (marigold) Lutemax 2020™ extract dry conc. 25 mg equivalent fresh flowers 4.2 g standardised to lutein 5 mg standardised to zeaxanthin 1 mg Vaccinium myrtillus (bilberry) extract dry concentrate 80 mg equivalent to fresh fruit 8 g standardised to anthocyanins 28.8 mg Colecalciferol 7.5 mg equivalent vitamin D3 300 IU Show More Omega + Vision Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Contacts & FAQs Report a Suspected Adverse Experience Contact Us Ask a Naturopath Product & Purchasing FAQs Blackmores Subscribe Contacts & FAQs R