urchase. Support For Immune System Health Energy Antioxidant for Free Radical Damage No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Specifically formulated with ‘Sustained Release Technology’ to provide lasting energy for up to 8 hours a day. Contains antioxidants that help to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Supports healthy immune system function. Supports energy production. Maintain nervous system health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 microgram for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Specifically formulated with ‘Sustained Release Technology’ to provide lasting energy for up to 8 hours a day. Contains antioxidants that help to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Supports healthy immune system function. Supports energy production. Maintain nervous system health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 microgram for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. Dietar