  ('e6d925ce-27d4-461c-8bb0-9e065a95298d'::uuid, 'manual', 'TH', null, 'Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil', 'blackmores_evening_primrose_oil_fish_oil', '40e4806a-5049-4668-8d29-ab36a31202dd'::uuid, 'blackmores', 'blackmores', 'https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/blt948bd74310fc0ad0/bltb0a0e334a5b30c2b/68bfb8ee5fb6b7184ce3df86/9300807003572-1.webp', 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/evening-primrose-oil-and-fish-oil', 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/evening-primrose-oil-and-fish-oil', 'Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil provides a daily dose of the recommended intake of omega-3 and omega-6 essential fatty acids.', null, 'Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil', null, 'Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil provides a daily dose of the recommended intake of omega-3 and omega-6 essential fatty acids.', null, null, null, 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/evening-primrose-oil-and-fish-oil', '{"dosage":"for use. Read the","locale":"en","parser":"blackmores_structured_ingredients_v2","titleEn":"Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil","htmlLength":166004,"validation":{"status":"pass","reasons":[],"summary":"2 matchable canonical facts.","checkedAt":"2026-05-21T13:36:41.294Z","matchableFactCount":2},"description":"Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil provides a daily dose of the recommended intake of omega-3 and omega-6 essential fatty acids.","descriptionEn":"Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil provides a daily dose of the recommended intake of omega-3 and omega-6 essential fatty acids.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil Size Size 100 capsules Good health changes everything—support skin and general wellbeing with Blackmores Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil. This dual formulation provides a blend of omega-6 and omega-3 essential fatty acids to maintain skin health and support general health and wellbeing. Evening primrose oil is a source of gamma-linolenic acid (GLA), while fish oil provides eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA). These essential fatty acids contribute to overall wellness and can be particularly helpful when dietary intake is inadequate. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Skin Health Inflammation Children&#x27;s Health Kids Development No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Gluten Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Source of omega-3 eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA), docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and omega-6 linoleic acid (LA) fatty acids. EPO is a source of GLA, the precursor of prostaglandins that play an important role in the body&#x27;s inflammatory response At higher dose it can help reduce inflammatory response. Important for structure and function of cell membranes. Important for maintenance of general health and wellbeing. Maintains skin health. Supports healthy growth and development in children when dietary intake is inadequate. Dosage Adults For general health and wellbeing: Take 3 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. For skin and as an anti-inflammatory: Take 7 capsules per day or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Children 3+ For healthy growth and development: Pierce and squeeze 2 capsules once a day into milk, juice or cereal and consume immediately, or as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your healthcare professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish products, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Source of omega-3 eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA), docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and omega-6 linoleic acid (LA) fatty acids. EPO is a source of GLA, the precursor of prostaglandins that play an important role in the body&#x27;s inflammatory response At higher dose it can help reduce inflammatory response. Important for structure and function of cell membranes. Important for maintenance of general health and wellbeing. Maintains skin health. Supports healthy growth and development in children when dietary intake is inadequate. Adults For general health and wellbeing: Take 3 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. For skin and as an anti-inflammatory: Take 7 capsules per day or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Children 3+ For healthy growth and development: Pierce and squeeze 2 capsules once a day into milk, juice or cereal and consume immediately, or as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your healthcare professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish products, soya bean products and sulfites. Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Evening primrose oil (EPO) 500 mg providing gamma-linolenic acid (GLA) 50 mg Fish oil - natural 500 mg containing omega-3 triglycerides 150 mg equivalent docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 60 mg equivalent eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 90 mg Evening Primrose Oil + Fish Oil Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHe