en under 18 years old Only as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Talk to your doctor before making any changes to heart medication. Do not take while on warfarin therapy without medical advice. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding consult your health professional before use. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites and soya bean products. Benefits Dosage Warnings CoQ10 is an antioxidant which helps reduce free radicals formed in the body. Helps in the maintenance of healthy blood lipids. Maintains CoQ10 levels in the body. 2 capsules a day: Maintains heart and blood vessel health. Supports healthy cardiovascular system function. Supports energy levels. Adults Take 1 capsule daily to support CoQ10 levels in the body. Take 2 capsules daily to heart and blood vessel health and energy levels. Children under 18 years old Only as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Talk to your doctor before making any changes to heart medication. Do not take while on warfarin therapy without medical advice. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding consult your health professional before use. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites and soya bean products. Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Ubidecarenone (Coenzyme Q10) 75 mg CoQ10 75mg Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Insta