;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Daily Immune Action Size Size 60 tablets Good health changes everything - support your immune system daily with Blackmores Daily Immune Action. This one-a-day formula combines vitamin C, vitamin D, zinc, and elderberry to help maintain immune system health and support healthy immune system function. Vitamin C and zinc also act as antioxidants to help reduce free radicals formed in the body. The formula helps maintain immune system to fight illness and supports general health and wellbeing. Elderberry adds a plant-based element to this immune-supporting blend, making it a suitable daily option for those seeking nutritional support for immune defence. With a convenient format and key nutrients, Blackmores Daily Immune Action is designed to support you year-round. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Immune System Health General Health Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Can be taken daily to support immune system health all year round. Maintains immune system to fight illness. Convenient one-a-day dose. Contains key immune nutrients vitamin C, D and zinc. Additional elderberry which is a source of vitamin C. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Can be taken daily to support immune system health all year round. Maintains immune system to fight illness. Convenient one-a-day dose. Contains key immune nutrients vitamin C, D and zinc. Additional elderberry which is a source of vitamin C. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 100 mg Colecalciferol 10 micrograms equivalent vitamin D3 400 IU Sambucus nigraa (elderberry) fruit juice conc. 143 mg equivalent fresh fruit juice 1 g Zinc sulfate monohydrate 41.6 mg equivalent zinc 15 mg Daily Immune Action Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blac