  ('ec476337-cff3-4cba-8b42-65342d964669'::uuid, 'manual', 'TH', null, 'Blackmores Mega B Complex', 'blackmores_mega_b_complex', '40e4806a-5049-4668-8d29-ab36a31202dd'::uuid, 'blackmores', 'blackmores', 'https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/blt948bd74310fc0ad0/blt83207a9ce866e09a/68bfbb849571c12a1f62df93/93808811-1.webp', 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/mega-b-complex', 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/mega-b-complex', 'Blackmores Mega B Complex supports energy, stress response, and skin health with essential B vitamins.', null, 'Blackmores Mega B Complex', null, 'Blackmores Mega B Complex supports energy, stress response, and skin health with essential B vitamins.', null, null, null, 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/mega-b-complex', '{"dosage":"for use. Read the","locale":"en","parser":"blackmores_structured_ingredients_v2","titleEn":"Blackmores Mega B Complex","htmlLength":178309,"validation":{"status":"pass","reasons":[],"summary":"10 matchable canonical facts.","checkedAt":"2026-05-22T00:29:44.183Z","matchableFactCount":10},"description":"Blackmores Mega B Complex supports energy, stress response, and skin health with essential B vitamins.","descriptionEn":"Blackmores Mega B Complex supports energy, stress response, and skin health with essential B vitamins.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Mega B Complex Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Mega B Complex Size Size 31 tablets 75 tablets 200 tablets Good health changes everything—support energy and vitality with Blackmores Mega B Complex so you can get the most out of your day. This high-strength blend of essential B vitamins helps maintain energy levels, support cognitive function, and assist healthy red blood cell production. It contributes to skin health, oral mucous membrane health, and hair health, while also helping to support a healthy stress response. Ideal for those managing a busy lifestyle or physical exertion, Blackmores Mega B Complex is formulated to help you stay energised throughout your day. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Energy Stress No Added Wheat No Added Gluten No Added Yeast No Added Soya Bean No Added Dairy Vegan Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Combination B vitamin formula. Supports energy levels & a healthy stress response in the body. Supports skin health. Assists healthy red blood cell production. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible. (Contains vitamin B6). Dietary supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Combination B vitamin formula. Supports energy levels & a healthy stress response in the body. Supports skin health. Assists healthy red blood cell production. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible. (Contains vitamin B6). Dietary supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Thiamine hydrochloride (vitamin B1) 50 mg Riboflavin (vitamin B2) 30 mg Nicotinamide 100 mg Calcium pantothenate 50 mg equivalent pantothenic acid (vitamin B5) 45.8 mg Pyridoxine hydrochloride 50 mg equivalent pyridoxine (vitamin B6) 41.1 mg Cyanocobalamin (vitamin B12) 50 micrograms Biotin 50 micrograms Choline bitartrate 50 mg Inositol 50 mg Folic acid 300 micrograms Show More Mega B Complex Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Contacts & FAQs Report a Suspected Adverse Experience Contact Us Ask a Naturopath Product & Purchasing FAQs Blackmores Subscribe Contacts & FAQs Report a Suspected Adverse Experience Contact Us Ask a Naturopath Product & Purchasing FAQs Blackmores Subscribe Back To Top Terms of Purchase Privacy Policy ©2025 Blackmores. All Rights Reserved. ©2025 Blackmores. All Rights Reserved.","productImportId":"c6370940-fb92-4544-a8a1-3f03ae584319","aiFactCorrection":{"notes":"Mapped noisy B-vitamin salts and equivalents to canonical catalogue entries using structured ingredients; reported vitamin-equivalent amounts for B5/B6; retained per-tablet doses.","responseId":"d8825d5e-f203-92f8-9fb9-c32e6649c9f0","correctedAt":"2