Products Favorite Pack World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Ask the Expert --> News & Activities Blackmores Video News & Activities Blackmores Video Ask the Expert --> World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Products Favorite Pack Healthy Tips Find Store  Log In Member Sign Up TH EN Health & Remedies      Health Hub       ALL Blackmores Marine Collagen Absolute About this product Hydrolyzed collagen with CoQ10, Lutein, Grape seed extract, Horsetail extract, and French maritime pine bark extract Zinc contributes to normal protein synthesis and maintenance of normal skin Features BLACKMORES MARINE COLLAGEN ABSOLUTE Dietary Supplement containing hydrolyzed collagen with CoQ10, lutein, grape seed extract, horsetail extract, French maritime pine bark extract, zinc which contributes to normal protein synthesis and maintenance of normal skin and selenium contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress. Dosage Adults – Take 1 capsule once a day. Take with food. Active ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Hydrolyzed marine fish collagen 250 mg   Lutein 20% and Zeaxanthin 1% 95.2 mg (provide Lutein 19 mg and Zeaxanthin 952 mcg) Grape seed extract 55 mg (equiv. to Vitis vinifera seed dry 6,600 mg)   Horsetail extract 50 mg (equiv. to Equisetum arvense stem dry 500 mg) Coenzyme Q10 25 mg   Nicotinamide 20 mg Zinc 15 mg (from Zinc amino acid chelate 20% 75 mg)   Natural vitamin E 10 IU (from d-alpha-Tocopheryl acetate 80% 9.17 mg) French maritime pine bark extract 5 mg (equiv. to Pinus pinaster bark dry 5,000 mg)   Selenium 26 mcg (from Selenomethionine 65 mcg) Available size 14, 30 and 60 capsules Cautions Read warning statement on a label before consume. No effect for prevention or cure diseases. Children and pregnant women should not be consumed. Should eat varieties of 5 categories food in appropriate proportion. ฆอ.3117/2564 | โฆษณานี้ได้รับการอนุญาตจาก