se. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding please talk with your health professional before use. WARNING: Contains zinc, which may be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Combines the benefits of vitamin C and zinc in one convenient supplement. Supports healthy immune function. Maintains zinc and vitamin C levels in the body. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1-2 tablets a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding please talk with your health professional before use. WARNING: Contains zinc, which may be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Zinc sulfate heptahydrate 100 mg equivalent zinc 22.7 mg Magnesium sulphate heptahydrate 50 mg equivalent magnesium 4.9 mg Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 250 mg ZinvitC250 Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People