Gluten free. Comes in a handbag friendly canister pack. Travel friendly, no refrigeration required. *Reid et al, FEMS immunol med microbiol 2003 35(2): 131-4 Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during first 3 months of pregnancy. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Contains clinically trialled* strains based on scientific evidence. 2.3 billion good bacteria per capsule. Helps support good vaginal bacteria levels. Maintains vaginal health. Gluten free. Comes in a handbag friendly canister pack. Travel friendly, no refrigeration required. *Reid et al, FEMS immunol med microbiol 2003 35(2): 131-4 Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during first 3 months of pregnancy. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Lactobacillus rhamnosus GR-1® 1.15 billion CFU Lactobacillus reuteri RC-14® 1.15 billion CFU Total good bacteria 2.3 billion CFU Probiotics+ Womens Flora Balance Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach