  ('fb9fdbb3-7522-493c-9c8a-33d9c79b528a'::uuid, 'manual', 'TH', null, 'C Acerola Plus', 'c_acerola_plus', '577a0c52-9c0a-44b8-b882-0f87363311a3'::uuid, 'swisse', 'swisse', 'http://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/Swisse-C-Acerola-1_8dabaab2-6156-4af8-b89c-35c6fee3b148.png?v=1757650952', 'https://swisse.co.th/products/c-acerola-plus', 'https://swisse.co.th/products/c-acerola-plus', 'Support radiant skin and collagen production with C Acerola Plus by Swisse. Ideal for beauty-conscious consumers in Thailand.', null, 'Swisse C Acerola Plus', 'สวิส ซี อะเซโรลา พลัส', 'Chewable tablets with acerola cherry concentrate providing natural vitamin C and supporting plant extracts.', 'เม็ดอมเคี้ยวที่มีสารสกัดจากอะเซโรลาเชอร์รี่ให้วิตามินซีธรรมชาติและสารสกัดจากพืชสนับสนุน', null, null, 'https://swisse.co.th/products/c-acerola-plus', '{"locale":"en","parser":"swisse_shopify_product_v1","titleEn":"Swisse C Acerola Plus","titleTh":"สวิส ซี อะเซโรลา พลัส","benefits":"Vitamin C contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress. Vitamin C contributes to normal collagen formation for the normal function of skin. Vitamin C contributes to the normal function of the immune system. Vitamin C contributes to normal energy yielding metabolism.","validation":{"status":"needs_review","reasons":["no_dosed_facts"],"summary":"No usable per-serving product facts.","checkedAt":"2026-05-22T00:31:49.686Z","matchableFactCount":0},"description":"Support radiant skin and collagen production with C Acerola Plus by Swisse. Ideal for beauty-conscious consumers in Thailand.","priceAmount":690,"descriptionEn":"Chewable tablets with acerola cherry concentrate providing natural vitamin C and supporting plant extracts.","descriptionTh":"เม็ดอมเคี้ยวที่มีสารสกัดจากอะเซโรลาเชอร์รี่ให้วิตามินซีธรรมชาติและสารสกัดจากพืชสนับสนุน","extractedText":"Swisse C Acerola Plus - Swisse Thailand Skip to content Products Back Products Beauty Eye Care Gummies Gut Health Immunity Joints, Bones, & Muscles Moisturisers Multivitamins Serums Skin Super Fruits & Herbs All Products Range Wellness Beauty Skincare About Back Our Story Ingredients Wellness Hub Sign in Search Cart (0) Cart empty Your cart is empty Continue shopping     svg]:w-full group-hover:text-uiGrey\"> Home / C Acerola Plus   Skip to product information Open media 1 in modal Open media 2 in modal Open media 3 in modal Swisse C Acerola Plus Swisse C Acerola Plus 2000 mg Chewable Tablets: A unique formula by Swisse, extracted from fresh Acerola cherries sourced from Brazil—the native origin of this powerful superfruit. Rich in vitamin C and high in antioxidants, it helps support overall health and immunity. Swisse committed to contributing positively to the needs of society and the planet, and we are the carbon neutral company. #CAcerolaPlus #Chewable Sale price 690 ฿ Where to buy Buy at TikTok Buy at Shopee Buy at Lazada Buy at Line Benefits Vitamin C contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress. Vitamin C contributes to normal collagen formation for the normal function of skin. Vitamin C contributes to the normal function of the immune system. Vitamin C contributes to normal energy yielding metabolism. Key Ingredients Acerola Conc. Powder 2000 mg Citrus bioflavonoid 25 mg Papaya ext. 10 mg Rose hip ext. 5 mg Grape seed ext. 5 mg Directions and Warnings DIRECTIONS: 1 tablets daily. Take during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. WARNINGS: Children, and pregnant women should not consume. Should eat a variety of the five categories of food in appropriate proportions. STORAGE: Store below 25C, in a cool, dry place. Do not use, if cap seal is broken. Reasons to love us We have been developing science-based formulas using premium ingredients sourced from around the world for over 50 years. We believe in natural ingredients being our hero ingredients. We also pursue the latest research findings to formulate our advanced product ranges and consistently strive to anticipate consumer demand. Backed by science Premium quality formula 50+ year heritage Certified B-Corp We are B-Corp Certified B Corps are for-profit companies that meet high standards of social and environmental performance, transparency, and accountability. Swisse is a brand of H&H Group, a certified B Corp. We feel honoured to be part of a global community using business as a force for good. Frequently Asked Questions Do we need to take vitamin supplements? The key is to ensure that we get a complete and balanced intake of nutrients each day. However, due to lifestyle limitations and dietary choices, we may not always receive the necessary nutrients in adequate amounts. In such cases, dietary supplements can be beneficial. Can Swisse products be taken alongside medication or medical treatments? Each individual has different nutritional and medicinal needs. If you are unsure whether Swisse products are suitable for you, it is best to consult a doctor. Please note that dietary supplements do not prevent, alter, or replace medical treatment or a well-balanced diet. What is the best time to take vitamins? Some supplements work best when taken with food, while others are more effective on an empty stomach. It is essential to follow the instructions on the label to maximize the benefits of each product. How long do dietary supplements last? In general, dietary supplements have a shelf life of approximately two years from the manufacturing date. Where does Swisse source its ingredients? We carefully select and source high-quality, premium-grade ingredients from around the world to ensure that only the best components go into our products. Where are Swisse products manufactured? Most of our products are manufactured in Australia. Please refer to the product packaging for the specific country of origin. The recommended dosage on the label applies to which age group? The recommended dosage is intended for individuals aged 18 and above. You may also like Swisse Vitamin C Sale price 590 ฿