  ('fbd5f451-d6bd-4749-bf31-06e76d51f9bd'::uuid, 'manual', 'TH', null, 'Blackmores Fall Asleep', 'blackmores_fall_asleep', '40e4806a-5049-4668-8d29-ab36a31202dd'::uuid, 'blackmores', 'blackmores', 'https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/blt948bd74310fc0ad0/bltb71ada960982a89f/68bfbf5c099797e42a5ef52a/93569828-1.webp', 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/fall-asleep', 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/fall-asleep', 'Blackmores Fall Asleep™ combines magnesium with traditional herbs including lemon balm and lavender.', null, 'Blackmores Fall Asleep', null, 'Blackmores Fall Asleep™ combines magnesium with traditional herbs including lemon balm and lavender.', null, null, null, 'https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/fall-asleep', '{"dosage":"for use. Read the","locale":"en","parser":"blackmores_structured_ingredients_v2","titleEn":"Blackmores Fall Asleep","htmlLength":168893,"validation":{"status":"pass","reasons":[],"summary":"1 matchable canonical fact.","checkedAt":"2026-05-22T00:29:13.053Z","matchableFactCount":1},"description":"Blackmores Fall Asleep™ combines magnesium with traditional herbs including lemon balm and lavender.","descriptionEn":"Blackmores Fall Asleep™ combines magnesium with traditional herbs including lemon balm and lavender.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Fall Asleep Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Fall Asleep Size Size 30 tablets 60 tablets Blackmores Fall Asleep™ contains a blend of magnesium and traditional herbs, including lemon balm, lavender and ziziphus. This formula is traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to aid mind relaxation, reduce symptoms of mild anxiety, and reduce time to fall asleep. It is also traditionally used in Chinese medicine to reduce disturbed sleep. Good health changes everything - start with Blackmores Fall Asleep™. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Sleep Nervous System Health Nervous Tension No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Lemon balm and lavender are traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to: Reduce time to fall asleep. Help mind relaxation. Lavender relieves symptoms of mild anxiety. Ziziphus is traditionally used in Chinese medicine to: Relieve disturbed and restless sleep. Help restore your body and recharge your batteries. Magnesium Supports nervous system function. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 2 tablets once a day, 30 minutes before bedtime. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Always talk to your health professional before taking multiple products to support sleep. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Lemon balm and lavender are traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to: Reduce time to fall asleep. Help mind relaxation. Lavender relieves symptoms of mild anxiety. Ziziphus is traditionally used in Chinese medicine to: Relieve disturbed and restless sleep. Help restore your body and recharge your batteries. Magnesium Supports nervous system function. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 2 tablets once a day, 30 minutes before bedtime. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Always talk to your health professional before taking multiple products to support sleep. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Lavandula angustifolia (lavender) extract dry conc. 150 mg equivalent dry flower 600 mg Magnesium phosphate pentahydrate 266 mg equivalent magnesium 55 mg Melissa officinalis (lemon balm) extract dry conc. 150 mg equivalent dry leaf 600 mg Ziziphus jujuba var spinosa (ziziphus) extract dry conc. 250 mg equivalent dry seed 5000 mg (5 g) Fall Asleep Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Appr